&lt;p&gt;Descriptions, ingredients, difficulty, and risk for all 66 alchemical formulae. Formula order matches &lt;code&gt;DARKLAND.LST&lt;/code&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;Canonical source: &lt;code&gt;darkland.alc.xml&lt;/code&gt; (wallace.net)&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
