&lt;td&gt;Base difficulty when mixing a new potion&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;
&lt;td&gt;+0x52&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td&gt;2&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td&gt;&lt;code&gt;risk_factor&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td&gt;Mixing risk: 0 = low, 1 = medium, 2 = high&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;
&lt;td&gt;+0x54&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td&gt;20&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td&gt;&lt;code&gt;ingredients[5]&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td&gt;Up to 5 required ingredients; unused slots are zeroed&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;/tbody&gt;
&lt;/table&gt;
