&lt;p&gt;Ingredients are listed in increasing item code order.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;Confidence&lt;span class="hx:absolute hx:-mt-20" id="confidence"&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;a href="#confidence" class="subheading-anchor" aria-label="Permalink for this section"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;Medium-high. Documented in &lt;code&gt;darkland.alc.xml&lt;/code&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Saints (DARKLAND.SNT)</title><link>https://arkana-mechanika-labs.github.io/formats/world-data/saints/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://arkana-mechanika-labs.github.io/formats/world-data/saints/</guid><description>
&lt;p&gt;Long text descriptions of all 136 saints, used in the in-game saint reference screen. Saint order matches &lt;code&gt;DARKLAND.LST&lt;/code&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;Canonical source: &lt;code&gt;darkland.snt.xml&lt;/code&gt; (wallace.net)&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;File Layout&lt;span class="hx:absolute hx:-mt-20" id="file-layout"&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;a href="#file-layout" class="subheading-anchor" aria-label="Permalink for this section"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;div class="hextra-code-block hx:relative hx:mt-6 hx:first:mt-0 hx:group/code"&gt;
&lt;div&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code&gt;Offset 0x00: byte num_saints = 136
Offset 0x01: string[136] saint_descriptions — fixed 360 bytes each&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="hextra-code-copy-btn-container hx:opacity-0 hx:transition hx:group-hover/code:opacity-100 hx:flex hx:gap-1 hx:absolute hx:m-[11px] hx:right-0 hx:top-0"&gt;
&lt;button
class="hextra-code-copy-btn hx:group/copybtn hx:cursor-pointer hx:transition-all hx:active:opacity-50 hx:bg-primary-700/5 hx:border hx:border-black/5 hx:text-gray-600 hx:hover:text-gray-900 hx:rounded-md hx:p-1.5 hx:dark:bg-primary-300/10 hx:dark:border-white/10 hx:dark:text-gray-400 hx:dark:hover:text-gray-50"
title="Copy code"
aria-label="Copy code"
data-copied-label="Copied!"
&gt;
&lt;div class="hextra-copy-icon hx:group-[.copied]/copybtn:hidden hx:pointer-events-none hx:h-4 hx:w-4"&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class="hextra-success-icon hx:hidden hx:group-[.copied]/copybtn:block hx:pointer-events-none hx:h-4 hx:w-4"&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/button&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Each description is a fixed &lt;strong&gt;360 byte (0x168)&lt;/strong&gt; null-padded string.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;Relationship to Other Files&lt;span class="hx:absolute hx:-mt-20" id="relationship-to-other-files"&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;a href="#relationship-to-other-files" class="subheading-anchor" aria-label="Permalink for this section"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;table&gt;
&lt;thead&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;
&lt;th&gt;File&lt;/th&gt;
&lt;th&gt;Saint data&lt;/th&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;/thead&gt;
&lt;tbody&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;
&lt;td&gt;&lt;code&gt;DARKLAND.LST&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td&gt;Full names (&lt;code&gt;St.…&lt;/code&gt;), short names (&lt;code&gt;S.…&lt;/code&gt;), definitive order&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;
&lt;td&gt;&lt;code&gt;DARKLAND.SNT&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td&gt;Long text descriptions (this file)&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;
&lt;td&gt;Save file &lt;code&gt;+0x80&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td&gt;160-bit bitmask per character; bit N = saint N is known&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;/tbody&gt;
&lt;/table&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;Confidence&lt;span class="hx:absolute hx:-mt-20" id="confidence"&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;a href="#confidence" class="subheading-anchor" aria-label="Permalink for this section"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;Medium-high. Documented in &lt;code&gt;darkland.snt.xml&lt;/code&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>